Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-a)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請D區150號之前的觀眾入場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易混亂受傷 所以請排隊入場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.29,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs42\shad0\c&H565959&\pos(374,222)}羽佐間正義先生的公寓發生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.29,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs42\shad0\c&H565959&\pos(376,272)}原因是天然氣洩露？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛朗明哥小哥還真是不小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人傷腦筋呢 這樣會損害麻里的形象的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為羽佐間先生在麻里拯救世界的時候出了一份力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的心目中已經被篡改成那樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「部下的過失是領隊的責任」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果別人這麼說了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是佛朗明哥少女團還是佛朗明哥現在都停業中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且事到如今也不會有人來抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生？那算什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 大家都被襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也要小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的大家也包括那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說後藤先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生這事先暫且不提 那邊你也好好做個了斷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼了斷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣下去你甘心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要問你 這樣下去你甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一起努力辦好演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MMM 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MMM 東京巨蛋 Live and Peace！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Live and Peace！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護車 快叫救護車！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0100,,告訴我什麼是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為服用了有毒的藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛為她們做了洗胃 現在需要觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說要調查過成分才能下結論 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在舉辦演唱會的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MMM的三澤瑞希和森田萌小姐在公演中突然倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們在開演前喝下了含有藥物的咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻里 現在無法接聽您的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在嗶聲後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 回個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的目的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只有我消失才能阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我令他變成那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個方法可以承擔責任……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛剛醒了 可以進去探望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非比常人的恢復力 不愧是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說想先和你單獨見一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 我們等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容整形應該去其他醫院才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老太婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 害您變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然犯人跟你有關的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「替我向佛朗明哥武士先生問好」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的紅斧之耳擁有常人7倍的聽力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實聽到了你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他了吧 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的紅斧之眼擁有常人12倍的視…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤田灰司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做澤田灰司 是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的文具不賣給警察嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些可以用來鎮壓暴徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上已經沒有暴徒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠川 之前的事你考慮過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養子的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得不太合適…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒 這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘 說到養子應該先找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小蒼太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H53B55B&\shad0\bord0\fs60}離 婚 申 請 書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤田灰司…這次出現了一個棘手的敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就像是在和幽靈戰鬥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在記錄上已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻接二連三地襲擊我身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果英雄陷入了危機 該向誰求助呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會尋求他人幫助的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦 無論遭遇多麼不講理的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必須自己承受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨才是我們真正的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛酸吧 很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 人類才時而會被邪惡所誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也正因如此 我們才握有絕對無敵的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在看來 你還沒有掌握它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父 請別說笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是在說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛是無窮無限的最強之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓人變得無比強大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果愛能成為正義的夥伴 那就什麼都不必害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掌握愛吧 羽佐間正義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂…我不懂啊 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼愛會使人變強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 要怎麼做才能掌握愛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這需要你自己領悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父！請別敷衍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我真沒辦法教你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為愛的形式和掌握它的要領都因人而異
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能告訴你的只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了 你們進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 看起來很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}要先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}小姐 肛門科不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我的肛門可是很健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談話結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Part-B)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.04,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz358.813\pos(612,548)\c&H363636&}小後。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.04,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz356.32\pos(536,578)\c&H363636&}這樣下去真的好嗎？(>_<)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.04,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz355.285\pos(506,610)\c&H363636&}你真的不再見正義了嗎？(T_T)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤 現在可是上班時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去挨家挨戶巡邏一下 這裡就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 媽媽抱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 我的腦子裡都只有英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不知道…什麼是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0700,0000,,正義 正義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0700,0000,0000,,愛…愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你從剛剛開始就不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼煩惱 就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得和你談也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 可以暫時別理我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機先生 我要更改目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 這個 這個 這個 還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你第一次上的雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是發給出版商的簡歷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加綜藝節目時的台本 當時的收視率表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訪談 海報和日曆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這是你出道時的第一張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看你這張臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容也很僵硬 比外行人還糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你也有自己的閃光點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始就很確定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擁有他人所沒有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個值得我賭一把的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都更早注視你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人我可是看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 佛朗明哥武士的事我一開始就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睜隻眼閉隻眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你就瞪鼻子上臉 從佛朗明哥變成了Flamenger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛朗明哥星人算什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的設計全都打亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和原定計畫偏了十萬八千里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我今後也想繼續關注你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果你有煩惱 就請告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為都燒光了 原來這個還留著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧了石原小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子不是死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他確實出現在我的周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父也說看到了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得他並不是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 還是第一次接到你主動打來的電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 而且我覺得這應該也是最後一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想請你幫我查一下一位名叫澤田灰司的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤田灰司？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察說他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你覺得警察都不知道的事情我會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然覺得你又討厭又煩人又難對付又讓人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你那可疑的情報網和行動力還是最讓人信賴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是至今為止最讓我高興的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我這就查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐 你好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是愛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒喜歡過女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止一次都沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 因為我一直忙於英雄的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐 愛是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很棒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再詳細點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法代替的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再具體點！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒法說具體…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛有很多種形式 沒法說清道明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父也是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他說只能自己掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在小時候都是由父母撫養的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說你是爺爺撫養的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爺爺想保護你的心情 這就是愛的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母相遇 想要共度人生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是一種愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:15:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的粉絲們為你加油打氣 這也是一種愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上充滿了愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有注意到的人就體會不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為 愛發生在不同人的身上 能輕易地變成其他的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成其他感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對英雄的感情 這也一定是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤田對你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸根到底也許也是一種愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是比喻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於不懂得愛的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會拘泥 執著 時而憤怒或是憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要照顧你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從某種意義上說或許也是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是從某種意義上說啊 某種意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛雖然很美好 但同時也很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家才會為此飽受折磨 卻仍然不懈追求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有愛也無所謂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了啊 你或許只是沒有發覺自己內心的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我內心的愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我找不到手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這才是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這也不是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}收到了「她」的短信
